Pendulum Effect
 Once per turn: You can pay 500 LP, then target 1 face-up monster your opponent controls; it loses 500 ATK. Unless you have a "DD" card in your other Pendulum Zone, this card's Pendulum Scale becomes 5.

 Monster Effect
 When this card is Normal Summoned: You can add 1 face-up DARK Pendulum Monster Card from your Extra Deck to your hand.
